simplehttpd - simple HTTP daemon
================================

[;37;41;1;5mNOT TO BE USED IN PRODUCTION ENVIRONMENTS[m

USAGE

    simplehttpd [-Cv] [-d docroot] [-l addr] [-p port]

OPTIONS

    -d path     docroot (default is ~/public_html)
    -h          display usage message
    -l address  listen on specified address
    -p port     listen on specified port
    -v          display version message

